N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 184.3 - Validity of rules and regulations

State Regulations

If any Part, section, paragraph, subdivision, clause or
provision of this Subchapter shall be adjudged invalid, such adjudication shall
apply only to the Part, section, paragraph, subdivision, clause, or provision
so adjudged, and the rest of this Subchapter shall be and remain valid and
effective. Notes
